The cumulative incidence of cases of coronavirus (COVID-19) shows a similar development in the European Union/the European Economic Space and the United Kingdom, confirming that, despite different stages, the COVID-19 pandemy is rapidly progressed in all countries.
According to Italy's experience, countries, hospitals and intensive care services must be prepared for a few patients with COVID-19 needing care, especially intensive care.
