In the framework of this study, we evaluate the development of the cumulative impact of the COVID-19 in each of the countries of the European Union/the European Economic Space (EU/EEA) and the United Kingdom (R.-U.) and compare it to the development of the province of Hubei in China.
We also compare the current number of cases of COVID-19 in EU/EE and the United Kingdom with Italy for the period from 31 January to 15 March 2020.
Cas de COVID-19 in EU/EEE countries and the United Kingdom
